column2: HI IM PLANNING A TRIP TO * LOCATIONS IN * DAYS CAN YOU HELP ME PLAN MY CLOTHING REQUIREMENTS
column5: Hi! I would love to help you plan your clothing. Please tell me the locations you will be visiting and the days you’ll be there. For example#Comma you could say: "I’ll be visiting Paris on Monday#Comma Tokyo on Tuesday#Comma etc.
